# ResearchPulse Environment Configuration
# ========================================
# This file contains SECRETS ONLY (API keys, passwords, credentials).
# Non-sensitive defaults are in:
#   - /config/defaults.yaml (project-level, overrides app defaults)
#   - /apps/<app>/config/defaults.yaml (app-level defaults)
#
# Configuration precedence (highest to lowest):
# 1. Environment variables (runtime override)
# 2. This file (.env) - secrets only
# 3. /config/defaults.yaml apps.<app> (project overrides)
# 4. /apps/<app>/config/defaults.yaml (app defaults)
# 5. Hardcoded Python defaults
#
# To customize non-sensitive settings (categories, URLs, timeouts, etc.):
#   - Edit /config/defaults.yaml for project-wide changes
#   - Or set environment variables at runtime

